Text: Are You SatisfiedTradingpst Dear Premiere Conferencing Customer Thank you for using our conferencing service We hope we met your needs and exceeded your expectations Please help us continue to improve our service by telling us a little about your conferencing experiencewe would greatly appreciate it if you would take a moment to fill out the following online questionnaire To participate in our brief question multiple choice survey please click on the following url surveycsssurveyasp Thank you for your valuable input Sincerely Michele Hayden VP Client Services Premiere Conferencing This message was sent by a Premiere Conferencing Enhanced Services client If you would prefer not to receive further messages from this sender Click on the Reply button Replace the Subject field with the word REMOVE Click the Send button You will receive one additional email message confirming your removal
